OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775747466
OL,3,CIran ceasefire 'hanging by a thread',
OL,4,Cas Israel continues to pound Lebanon
OL,6,FIt was always going to be a precarious
OL,7,Fceasefire, but in the space of one day
OL,8,Fit's barely holding.
OL,10,FEven the first round of talks to
OL,11,Fdiscuss a more sustainable peace are
OL,12,Fstarting to look unlikely.
OL,14,FThe Israeli attacks on Lebanon, one
OL,15,Fafter another, are destroying lives,
OL,16,Fhomes and buildings and weakening the
OL,17,Fchances of a sustainable peace for
OL,18,Fthis region.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
