OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775747466
OL,3,CIran ceasefire 'hanging by a thread',
OL,4,Cas Israel continues to pound Lebanon
OL,6,FWhen the deal was announced on Tuesday
OL,7,Fnight, the tweet from the Pakistani
OL,8,FPrime Minister was clear that an
OL,9,Fimmediate ceasefire had been agreed
OL,10,Fbetween the United States, Iran and
OL,11,Ftheir allies.
OL,13,FHe went onto confirm it was an
OL,14,Fimmediate ceasefire everywhere,
OL,15,Fincluding Lebanon and elsewhere,
OL,16,Feffective immediately.
OL,18,FIt seems, despite being so keen on
OL,19,Fsocial media, that message didn't
OL,20,Freach US President Donald Trump or his
OL,21,FIsraeli allies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
