PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1775747466
OL,3,CIran ceasefire 'hanging by a thread',
OL,4,Cas Israel continues to pound Lebanon
OL,6,FThis evening, the White House is
OL,7,Freportedly saying that Lebanon is not
OL,8,Fpart of the deal.
OL,10,FThe problem is that Iran certainly
OL,11,Fbelieves it is, and this whole 14 day
OL,12,Fpause is now hanging by a thread.
OL,14,FEven the greatest pessimists, or those
OL,15,Fwho have covered such moments before,
OL,16,Fwould struggle to believe within 12
OL,17,Fhours more than 80 could be dead and
OL,18,Fover 700 injured.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
