OL,3,CIran ceasefire 'hanging by a thread',
OL,4,Cas Israel continues to pound Lebanon
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThis afternoon, a source close to
OL,12,FHezbollah told me that if the attacks
OL,13,Fdid not stop, the Strait of Hormuz
OL,14,Fwould not reopen.
OL,16,FIn reality this whole deal hinges on
OL,17,Fthat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
