OL,3,CIran ceasefire 'hanging by a thread',
OL,4,Cas Israel continues to pound Lebanon
OL,6,FA second source, here in Tehran, told
OL,7,Fme that urgent contact was being made
OL,8,Fwith the Pakistani interlocutors to
OL,9,Furge them to demand Israel respect the
OL,10,Fdeal which had been agreed.
OL,12,FFor the Iranians, an end to attacks
OL,13,Fwas a key point.
OL,15,FThis the exact wording sent to me by
OL,16,Fan Iranian official from the ten
OL,17,Fagreed points put by the Iranians:
OL,18,F"Complete cessation of any aggression
OL,19,Fagainst Iran and allied resistance
OL,20,Fgroups."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
